OL,3,CPride of Britain Fundraiser Finalist
OL,4,C2024: Jason Rostron
OL,6,FGuernsey's Jason Rostron has been
OL,7,Fnominated for a Pride of Britain
OL,8,FRegional Fundraiser of the Year Award.
OL,10,FSince last September, Jason has raised
OL,11,Falmost #4,500 for a number of
OL,12,Fdifferent, locally-based charities
OL,13,Fthrough 'bike night' events during the
OL,14,Fsummer months.
OL,16,FMore than a decade since the first
OL,17,Fevent took place, Jason has brought in
OL,18,Fand donated #50,000 to good causes but
OL,19,Fhe says it can be hard to choose the
OL,20,Frecipients when so many need help.
