OL,3,CPride of Britain Fundraiser Finalist
OL,4,C2024: Jason Rostron
OL,6,FHe explains: "We hand choose the
OL,7,Fcharity and trust me, we are getting
OL,8,Finundated with people wanting help.
OL,9,FIt's really sad that we can't help
OL,10,Feveryone. But we try and do charities
OL,11,Fthat mean something personally to us.
OL,13,F"Headway helped one of our fallen
OL,14,Fmembers many years ago so out of
OL,15,Frespect, we help them back. Grow
OL,16,FLimited, Priaulx Premature Baby
OL,17,FFoundation, Dementia Friendly Guernsey
OL,18,Fand the local lifeboat we do most
OL,19,Fyears, unless there's something really
OL,20,Furgent and important happening."
