OL,4,C2024: Jason Rostron
OL,6,FThe 'bike nights' are held at
OL,7,FGuernsey's White Rock on the second
OL,8,FWednesday of every month during the
OL,9,Fsummer.
OL,11,FIt is an opportunity for dozens of
OL,12,Fmotorbike owners to bring their
OL,13,Fbeloved two-wheelers and have them
OL,14,Fadmired by islanders.
OL,16,FJason and his team of helpers then
OL,17,Fwalk through the crowds with donation
OL,18,Fbuckets.
