OL,3,CPride of Britain Fundraiser Finalist
OL,4,C2024: Jason Rostron
OL,6,FIf someone had said when he was
OL,7,Fsetting up the first 'bike night' 11
OL,8,Fyears ago that he would now have
OL,9,Fraised #50,000, he would not have
OL,10,Fbelieved it.
OL,12,FJason adds: "I'm just overwhelmed with
OL,13,Fthe response and I have to thank
OL,14,Feveryone for their generosity because
OL,15,Fit's mind-blowing what we've done.
OL,17,F"We've really made bonds with these
OL,18,Fcharities. They're so appreciative, I
OL,19,Fdidn't expect that side of it and it's
OL,20,Fvery, very humbling."
