OL,6,FShe says: "It's lovely when you know
OL,7,Fthat you're going to get money coming
OL,8,Fin because you can plan where you're
OL,9,Fgoing to spend it. We speak regularly
OL,10,Fwith the neonatal unit at the PEH
OL,11,F(Princess Elizabeth Hospital). The
OL,12,Fmoney is always well needed.
OL,14,F"We need people like Jason because we
OL,15,Fmake great relationships with them.
OL,16,FThey know what the charity needs and
OL,17,Fhow much we need the money.
