OL,6,FTo Jason directly, Jo had this
OL,7,Fmessage: "Well done and thank you for
OL,8,Fwhat you do for the island. I think
OL,9,Fhe's been supporting our charity for
OL,10,Fprobably eight or nine years now, it's
OL,11,Fphenomenal what he's done."
OL,13,FThe regional winner will be announced
OL,14,Fduring ITV Channel's 6pm news
OL,15,Fprogramme on Friday 20 September 2024
OL,16,Ffollowing a judging process.
